Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back against the wall... I \Nmean, how could I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This wasn't supposed to \Nhappen," I keep denying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just disappear... \NI can't stand myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping around, spouting lies, \Ngrieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold on desperately to these \Nfeelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does this stupid \Nguilt refuse to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffocate under its weight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clinging selfishly to \Nthe hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10: Peter Grill \Nand the Angry Megaton Axe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the two of you members \Nof the royal family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're kidding, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two warriors came waltzing\Ninto the Guild outta nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And now you're telling \Nme that they're royalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For the love of God, say something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did you hear such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer my question \Nwith another question!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one in charge of this interrogation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't very well lie about \Nsomething like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Lisa Alpacas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,acknowledge my position as the crown princess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Ogrestan and heir apparent to the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the reception desk for the\NYakeppachi Warriors Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What breathtaking pecs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dreamy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Antonio Spartokos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to submit an inquiry regarding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Mitchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got any work for us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady Mimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I barely recognized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is serious, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to get the princess \Nof a foreign country pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd cause an international \Ndisaster of epic proportions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your concern is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my word that my identity\Nshall pose no risk to you whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I desire is your creamy \Ngoodness, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I become pregnant with\Na child of unmatched strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall promptly disappear from your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thereafter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall never disclose \Nthe name of the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the interest of increasing our chances,\Nhow about we put a little more bump into our grind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Lady Mimi, Lady \NLisa ought to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Twas a long and arduous journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years since the day\Nthat they suddenly vanished,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,setting out on a mission to hone their\Nskills and leaving behind naught but a note...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, over the course \Nof those three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my feelings have not \Nwavered in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get off of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with that nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, the heart of Spartokos\Nbelongs only to Lady Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LADY LISA...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're the guy from...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU BASTARD...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING TO LADY LISA?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You destroyed my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll never get my security deposit back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SAVE YOUR EXCUSES!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much of a weapon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't fight back, he's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Lisa was almost certainly\Nnot the woman you named as your lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU DARE LAY A HAND ON HER?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reason with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how closely I follow his movements,\Nthere's only so much a banana can take...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Lisa Alpacas,\NCrown Princess of Ogrestan, I hereby command you:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease this senseless violence immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of pure hatred emanating\Nfrom this man is insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme get this straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ogre is an old friend of yours...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's had a crush on Big \NSis since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been chasin' her our whole lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have blossomed into a \Nbeautiful woman, Lady Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming there's a reason that you traveled\Nout of your way to a place such as this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a swift end to your mission\Nand return to our homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our armies are struggling with\Nthe absense of their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, even the most loyal\Nof Ogrestan's soldiers shall...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head, Spartokos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suffering of our soldiers \Nweighs heavily on my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I cannot afford to return just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, my three-year quest for\Nadventure led me to this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have selected Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest warrior on the planet,\Nas the official "donor"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destiny as a species is to strive for\Na generation more powerful than the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is especially important given my\Nfuture as the leader of Ogrestan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I am determined not\Nto return to our motherland
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until I carry the world's \Nstrongest child inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Lady Lisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Spartokos, have admired \Nyou since our tender youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, I devoted myself to\Ntraining in the art of combat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as to become a man \Nworthy of your affection
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is simple.\Nso as to become a man worthy of your affection
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ogre like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is exceedingly weaker than one such as I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that's brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such was the root of the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had there been a single man in Ogrestan\Nstrong enough to meet my standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would not have needed \Nto embark on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do indeed care \Nabout me, then I urge you:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prove your worth as a \Nprogenitor of our species...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spartokos I left behind in our\Nhomeland led a life of incompetence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unable to surpass your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become a man \Nworthy of your affection,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have devoted the past three years to an\Neven more difficult training regimen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I stand before you\Nhaving refined my combat prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to demonstrate \Nthe fruits of my labor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the honor of standing \Nat Lady Lisa's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?\NI challenge you to a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently someone challenged that dude who\Nwon the Grand Fighting Tournament to a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this whole thing \Nstarted because of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if memory serves, doesn't \NPeter Grill have a fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the challenger has a\Npersonal stake in this duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, "Defeat the strongest man alive,\Nbecome famous, and propose to the girl," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Sir Peter agreed \Nto this fight despite
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that there's \Nnothing in it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I win the match, it's \Nnot gonna change anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to end up losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos-kun would take\NLisa back home to their country...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would leave one less obstacle in the way\Nof my relationship with Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I gotta do is throw the match...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you were my \Nbiggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till death do us part, \Nlet's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And find no one like you
